Package: repo2cp
Title: Process Publication Repository Data into Citeproc Compatible Format
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ryan", "Raaum", , "ryan.raaum@lehman.cuny.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4723-5475"))
Description: Tools for processing bibliographic item data from online 
              publication, citation, and scholarship databases into citeproc-json, 
              an R list format that is a direct match, and a more database
              compatible list format. Includes tools to process listings from 
              PubMed (XML), Crossref, and OpenAlex.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
